-- UniCredit Reaches Agreement With Labor Unions on Job Reductions in Italy
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-10-18T06:33:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/unicredit-reaches-agreement-with-labor-unions-on-job-reductions-in-italy.html
 UniCredit SpA agreed with unions on
job reductions in Italy with 3,000 employes leaving the company
by 2013, according to a statement from labor union FALCRI.  A total of 4,700 will leave the bank over the next five
years, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
